      • getReceipt

        public java.lang.String getReceipt()
        Creates a list of all the items in the order, while calculating the total. The US Dollar sign, '$', is affixed to all prices.
        Returns:
        A formatted list of all the items and prices; it also returns the total.

        menu - The Menu for the items in the order.
